sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference Servers
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos Querier<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Collector as WVA Collector
    participant SatEngine as WVA Saturation Engine<br/>(30s loop)
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Controller as WVA Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Actuator as WVA Actuator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA

    Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Decision

    vLLM->>Prom: Expose KV cache utilization,<br/>queue depth, request counts
    SatEngine->>Collector: Trigger metric collection
    Collector->>Prom: PromQL queries<br/>HTTPS/9091, Bearer Token (SA token)
    Prom-->>Collector: vLLM saturation metrics<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Collector-->>SatEngine: Parsed replica-level metrics
    SatEngine->>SatEngine: Run analyzer<br/>(V1/V2/Queueing Model)
    SatEngine->>Cache: Write scaling decision<br/>(desiredOptimizedAlloc)
    SatEngine->>Actuator: Emit Prometheus gauges
    Note right of Actuator: wva_desired_replicas<br/>wva_current_replicas<br/>wva_desired_ratio
    Controller->>Cache: Read scaling decision
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update VariantAutoscaling status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Prom->>Actuator: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    HPA->>Prom: Query WVA metrics<br/>HTTPS/9091, Bearer Token
    HPA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment/LWS<br/>via scale subresource<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero

    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>(Gateway API Inference Extension)
    participant SFZ as WVA Scale-from-Zero Engine<br/>(100ms poll)
    participant DActuator as WVA Direct Actuator

    EPP->>EPP: Queue pending requests<br/>in flow control queue
    SFZ->>EPP: Scrape queue metrics<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token (epp-metrics-token)
    EPP-->>SFZ: Flow control queue size > 0
    SFZ->>SFZ: Detect scale-from-zero needed<br/>(zero replicas + pending requests)
    SFZ->>DActuator: Trigger direct scale
    DActuator->>K8sAPI: Patch scale subresource<br/>(replicas: 0 → minReplicas)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    SFZ->>Cache: Write decision to cache
